{"tid":1755184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動 - 聖誕節/新年，賀佢老母(21/12 - 1/1)","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T09:02:08.000Z","uid":108757,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8284018582575260432d8537e9b6dd6125f72d","tid":1755184,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">近期活動︰</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>11月28號</strong><br />\n突發 今個星期四有野要做！全世界入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754565</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>11月29號</strong><br />\n[行動] 11.29 我們都是鄭文傑 聲援集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754548</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>12月2號-6號</strong><br />\n突發！！！廣告界正式宣佈罷工！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755050</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>12月8號</strong><br />\n12月8 民陣吹大雞 國際人權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742159</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[行動建議]</span><br />\n<strong>12月21號-1月1號</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聖誕節/新年，賀佢老母</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84sRXeT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84sRXeT.png&h=6931a977&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYR3Omy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYR3Omy.png&h=a7a4b6eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n天時地利人和，罷四日工等於罷兩個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁好嘅機會邊度搵！<br />\n如果工會進度良好，到時應該可以組識到真正自發罷工，再加黎明行動，再加多區開花，我要見到聖誕節+新年，香港變死城！賀佢老母！<br />\n<br />\n如果同意請文宣準備吹大雞！細節、日期、時間慢慢再定！"},{"pid":"0be52f7bf05961411fe7a092725056afc0c4909a","tid":1755184,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07a0419fac9b5dc5297d950ac8079b83989968b","tid":1755184,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d1e889e5efb470d8b770d0d5999b0ffd4d35a6","tid":1755184,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"工會準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【突發】工會要人！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707695</a>"},{"pid":"253300f7dcd361e7a276bf10ba4e34c700d08cae","tid":1755184,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"慢慢推，有排<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62de17883d4bda5ce32ea08d05ab26a56190247f","tid":1755184,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"罷工？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要罷埋消費！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕仲行大商場？仲買聖誕優惠？仲買貴價貨？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不了！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今個聖誕！我地不快樂！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今個聖誕！我地唔慶祝！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今個聖誕！我地罷消費！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" cl